input_text.Prompt: Can you tell me how to see page likes on facebook?
input_text.Response A: Sure! I’m happy to help you. If you go to your profile page and click on the “Like” button, you can see the people who like your page.
input_text.Response B: To see your page likes on Facebook, go to your Facebook page and click on the 'Likes' button in the left-hand menu. From there, you can see the total number of likes your page has, as well as a breakdown of where those likes are coming from. You can also access a more detailed view by clicking on 'See All' under the 'Likes' button.

label_annotations.feedback: Response A is too short although factual. Response B is very good in that it answers the question but then elaborates on it  to give more information.
